            "title": "没品+4chan笑话集：赏菊无数，方成局长",
            "summary": "<p>没品选段</p>\n<p>宇航员克里斯蒂娜·科赫（Christina Koch）正式成为了人类史上离厨房最远的女性。<br>——<a href=\"https://www.sickipedia.net/User/talon\">talon</a></p>\n",
            "content_html": "<p>没品选段</p>\n<p>宇航员克里斯蒂娜·科赫（Christina Koch）正式成为了人类史上离厨房最远的女性。<br>——<a href=\"https://www.sickipedia.net/User/talon\">talon</a></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n<figure class=\"post__image post__image--center\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/Yue-Qiu-Mi-Mi.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"501\" height=\"449\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Yue-Qiu-Mi-Mi-xs.png 640w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Yue-Qiu-Mi-Mi-sm.png 768w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Yue-Qiu-Mi-Mi-md.png 1024w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Yue-Qiu-Mi-Mi-lg.png 1366w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Yue-Qiu-Mi-Mi-xl.png 1600w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Yue-Qiu-Mi-Mi-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>\n<p>我有整整14年没有碰过酒了。<br>直到我15岁。<br>——<a href=\"https://www.sickipedia.net/User/niggerfarage\">niggerfarage</a></p>\n<p>当两个孕妇打架的时候，她们其实是变成了“机动战士高达”。<br data-rich-text-line-break=\"true\">——<a href=\"https://www.sickipedia.net/User/blackdragon\">blackdragon</a></p>\n<p>医生们都管这叫“医学奇迹”，说我老婆是全世界第一个从这种寄生虫病里活下来的人。<br>那条钻进她脑壳里的“食脑虫”，没过多久就饿死了。<br>——<a href=\"https://www.sickipedia.net/User/wasp\">wasp</a></p>\n<figure class=\"post__image post__image--center\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/Ye-Su-Fu-Huo.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"497\" height=\"580\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Ye-Su-Fu-Huo-xs.png 640w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Ye-Su-Fu-Huo-sm.png 768w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Ye-Su-Fu-Huo-md.png 1024w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Ye-Su-Fu-Huo-lg.png 1366w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Ye-Su-Fu-Huo-xl.png 1600w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Ye-Su-Fu-Huo-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>\n<p>2008年在泰国度假时，我简直不敢相信自己的眼睛：那宽大的下巴，那方正的脸廓，还有那根硕大如马腿般的巨型老二……我当时脱口而出：“那绝对是个纯爷们儿，宝贝！”<br data-rich-text-line-break=\"true\">我就那样坐在曼谷的酒吧里，一杯接一杯地猛灌，试图让自己别去想电视里正播的内容——米歇尔·奥巴马大选获胜的画面。<br data-rich-text-line-break=\"true\">*传言称米歇尔奥巴马实际上是男性MTF*<br data-rich-text-line-break=\"true\">——<a href=\"https://www.sickipedia.net/User/wasp\">wasp</a></p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/Zheng-Que-Yu-Fou.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1792\" height=\"2368\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Zheng-Que-Yu-Fou-xs.png 640w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Zheng-Que-Yu-Fou-sm.png 768w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Zheng-Que-Yu-Fou-md.png 1024w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Zheng-Que-Yu-Fou-lg.png 1366w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Zheng-Que-Yu-Fou-xl.png 1600w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Zheng-Que-Yu-Fou-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>\n<hr>\n<h5>1、神奇动物</h5>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/Shen-Qi-Dong-Wu.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1144\" height=\"8442\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Shen-Qi-Dong-Wu-xs.png 640w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Shen-Qi-Dong-Wu-sm.png 768w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Shen-Qi-Dong-Wu-md.png 1024w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Shen-Qi-Dong-Wu-lg.png 1366w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Shen-Qi-Dong-Wu-xl.png 1600w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Shen-Qi-Dong-Wu-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>\n<h5>2、月之暗面</h5>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/Yue-Zhi-An-Mian.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1144\" height=\"1870\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Yue-Zhi-An-Mian-xs.png 640w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Yue-Zhi-An-Mian-sm.png 768w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Yue-Zhi-An-Mian-md.png 1024w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Yue-Zhi-An-Mian-lg.png 1366w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Yue-Zhi-An-Mian-xl.png 1600w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Yue-Zhi-An-Mian-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>\n<h5>3、人在囧途</h5>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/Ren-Zai-Jiong-Tu.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1142\" height=\"2379\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Ren-Zai-Jiong-Tu-xs.png 640w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Ren-Zai-Jiong-Tu-sm.png 768w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Ren-Zai-Jiong-Tu-md.png 1024w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Ren-Zai-Jiong-Tu-lg.png 1366w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Ren-Zai-Jiong-Tu-xl.png 1600w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Ren-Zai-Jiong-Tu-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>\n<h5>4、惊世智慧</h5>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/Liang-Shi-Zhi-Hui.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1142\" height=\"1971\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Liang-Shi-Zhi-Hui-xs.png 640w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Liang-Shi-Zhi-Hui-sm.png 768w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Liang-Shi-Zhi-Hui-md.png 1024w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Liang-Shi-Zhi-Hui-lg.png 1366w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Liang-Shi-Zhi-Hui-xl.png 1600w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Liang-Shi-Zhi-Hui-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>\n<h5>5、真假恐龙</h5>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/Zhen-Jia-Kong-Long.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1142\" height=\"7067\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Zhen-Jia-Kong-Long-xs.png 640w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Zhen-Jia-Kong-Long-sm.png 768w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Zhen-Jia-Kong-Long-md.png 1024w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Zhen-Jia-Kong-Long-lg.png 1366w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Zhen-Jia-Kong-Long-xl.png 1600w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Zhen-Jia-Kong-Long-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>\n<h5>6、牛李之争</h5>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/Niu-Li-Dang-Zheng.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1144\" height=\"4089\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Niu-Li-Dang-Zheng-xs.png 640w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Niu-Li-Dang-Zheng-sm.png 768w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Niu-Li-Dang-Zheng-md.png 1024w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Niu-Li-Dang-Zheng-lg.png 1366w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Niu-Li-Dang-Zheng-xl.png 1600w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Niu-Li-Dang-Zheng-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>\n<p>最后放一张看到的讨论，这绝对是我见过最他妈巨魔的发言了：</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/Ju-Mo-tedtalk.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1303\" height=\"696\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Ju-Mo-tedtalk-xs.png 640w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Ju-Mo-tedtalk-sm.png 768w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Ju-Mo-tedtalk-md.png 1024w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Ju-Mo-tedtalk-lg.png 1366w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Ju-Mo-tedtalk-xl.png 1600w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/responsive/Ju-Mo-tedtalk-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>\n<hr>\n<p>最后gif：</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/4/Peng-Peng-Peng.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"240\" height=\"418\"></figure>",
