        {
            "id": "https://www.meipin.im/mei-pin-4chanxiao-hua-jimo-liao-nan-niang-de-ou-pai-suan-bu-suan-gayni.html",
            "url": "https://www.meipin.im/mei-pin-4chanxiao-hua-jimo-liao-nan-niang-de-ou-pai-suan-bu-suan-gayni.html",
            "title": "没品+4chan笑话集：摸了男娘的欧派算不算gay呢？",
            "summary": "<p>没品选段</p>\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">☆ 我在公交车站溜达到一个陌生女人面前，对她说道：“打扰一下，亲爱的，你喜欢看《怪奇物语》（Stranger Things）吗？”<br><br>是的，我喜欢。她回答道。</p>\n",
            "content_html": "<p>没品选段</p>\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">☆ 我在公交车站溜达到一个陌生女人面前，对她说道：“打扰一下，亲爱的，你喜欢看《怪奇物语》（Stranger Things）吗？”<br><br>是的，我喜欢。她回答道。</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><br>于是我掏出了我的老二和蛋蛋。<br>——<a href=\"https://www.sickipedia.net/User/lennyscrevasse\">lennyscrevasse</a></p>\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">☆ 伦敦地下的老鼠家族十分反感地发现，这座城市竟然泛滥着政客。<br>——<a href=\"https://www.sickipedia.net/User/innit\">innit</a></p>\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><em>在阿尔忒弥斯2号绕月的同时：</em></p>\n<figure class=\"post__image post__image--center\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/Yue-Qiu-Shi-You.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"494\" height=\"505\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Yue-Qiu-Shi-You-xs.png 640w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Yue-Qiu-Shi-You-sm.png 768w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Yue-Qiu-Shi-You-md.png 1024w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Yue-Qiu-Shi-You-lg.png 1366w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Yue-Qiu-Shi-You-xl.png 1600w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Yue-Qiu-Shi-You-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">☆ 鸡肉现在实在太贵了，我已经开始抓海鸥当饭吃了。</p>\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">不过你下锅一定要快，不然它们会把你的薯条全给偷吃光。<br>——<a href=\"https://www.sickipedia.net/User/stickyagain\">stickyagain</a></p>\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><br>☆ 唐纳德·特朗普将于四月会晤英国国王和王后。</p>\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">我倒更希望他在下个月的某个时候，去见见上一任女王。<br>——<a href=\"https://www.sickipedia.net/User/niggerfarage\">niggerfarage</a></p>\n<figure class=\"post__image post__image--center\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/Huo-Er-Mu-Zi.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"505\" height=\"754\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Huo-Er-Mu-Zi-xs.png 640w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Huo-Er-Mu-Zi-sm.png 768w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Huo-Er-Mu-Zi-md.png 1024w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Huo-Er-Mu-Zi-lg.png 1366w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Huo-Er-Mu-Zi-xl.png 1600w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Huo-Er-Mu-Zi-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">☆ 我的卫生纸用完了，所以我只好拿旧报纸来凑合。<br>那个“时代”可真难用啊。<br>——<a href=\"https://www.sickipedia.net/User/innit\">innit</a></p>\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><br>☆ 听信征兵宣传去参军，就像觉得脱衣舞娘是真心看上了你一样。</p>\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">*新闻：将赴战场美军士兵被曝出在脱衣舞俱乐部挥霍*<br>——<a href=\"https://www.sickipedia.net/User/hoffmanassassian\">hoffmanassassian</a></p>\n<hr>\n<h5>1、深柜品如</h5>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/Shen-Ju-Pin-Ru.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1146\" height=\"4901\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Shen-Ju-Pin-Ru-xs.png 640w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Shen-Ju-Pin-Ru-sm.png 768w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Shen-Ju-Pin-Ru-md.png 1024w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Shen-Ju-Pin-Ru-lg.png 1366w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Shen-Ju-Pin-Ru-xl.png 1600w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Shen-Ju-Pin-Ru-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>\n<h5>2、恐龙效应</h5>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/Kong-Long-Xiao-Ying.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1144\" height=\"4980\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Kong-Long-Xiao-Ying-xs.png 640w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Kong-Long-Xiao-Ying-sm.png 768w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Kong-Long-Xiao-Ying-md.png 1024w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Kong-Long-Xiao-Ying-lg.png 1366w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Kong-Long-Xiao-Ying-xl.png 1600w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Kong-Long-Xiao-Ying-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>\n<h5>3、重音Pearto</h5>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/Li-Yin-teto.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1146\" height=\"1515\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Li-Yin-teto-xs.png 640w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Li-Yin-teto-sm.png 768w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Li-Yin-teto-md.png 1024w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Li-Yin-teto-lg.png 1366w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Li-Yin-teto-xl.png 1600w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Li-Yin-teto-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>\n<p>因为真的很可爱，所以我把原图放上来大家自取：</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/Li-Yin.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"990\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Li-Yin-xs.jpg 640w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Li-Yin-sm.jpg 768w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Li-Yin-md.jpg 1024w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Li-Yin-lg.jpg 1366w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Li-Yin-xl.jpg 1600w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Li-Yin-2xl.jpg 1920w\"></figure>\n<h4>4、成长意义</h4>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/Cheng-Chang-Yi-Yi.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1146\" height=\"2395\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Cheng-Chang-Yi-Yi-xs.png 640w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Cheng-Chang-Yi-Yi-sm.png 768w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Cheng-Chang-Yi-Yi-md.png 1024w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Cheng-Chang-Yi-Yi-lg.png 1366w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Cheng-Chang-Yi-Yi-xl.png 1600w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Cheng-Chang-Yi-Yi-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>\n<h5>5、超人归来</h5>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/Chao-Ren-Gui-Lai.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1146\" height=\"2795\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Chao-Ren-Gui-Lai-xs.png 640w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Chao-Ren-Gui-Lai-sm.png 768w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Chao-Ren-Gui-Lai-md.png 1024w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Chao-Ren-Gui-Lai-lg.png 1366w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Chao-Ren-Gui-Lai-xl.png 1600w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Chao-Ren-Gui-Lai-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>\n<h5>6、奥运阿福</h5>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/Ao-Yun-A-Fu.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1148\" height=\"4922\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Ao-Yun-A-Fu-xs.png 640w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Ao-Yun-A-Fu-sm.png 768w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Ao-Yun-A-Fu-md.png 1024w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Ao-Yun-A-Fu-lg.png 1366w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Ao-Yun-A-Fu-xl.png 1600w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/Ao-Yun-A-Fu-2xl.png 1920w\"></figure>\n<p>来到了4ch笑话集的大家真的还有人不认识阿福吗？为了防止还真有放一张图：</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image post__image--center\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/astolf.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"431\" height=\"647\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/astolf-xs.webp 640w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/astolf-sm.webp 768w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/astolf-md.webp 1024w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/astolf-lg.webp 1366w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/astolf-xl.webp 1600w ,https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/responsive/astolf-2xl.webp 1920w\"></figure>\n<hr>\n<p>最后gif：</p>\n<p>正部级狗狗</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image post__image--center\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://www.meipin.im/media/posts/3/Da-Kang-Gou-Gou.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"384\" height=\"360\"></figure>",
